page_0: "All this fighting and bickering is too much for this old Hammerite. The Commander I fear has lost his wits entirely. He has become reclusive and quick to anger. I only feel sorry for his new fianc‚e, she is feeling his wrath more than anyone.

As soon as this business with Grent is dealt with, I think I shall return to the City. At least my brethren will welcome me, though it pains me to abandon the Builder's church here at Sturmdrang.

Before I go I shall recover that pirate's crystal hidden in the crypt. It should make a worthy tithe for my troubles. Must remember the correct order.

Second floor south, fourth floor north, second floor north, first floor south. Yes, that was it. Well, I can always start again if I get it wrong."
